Text.val: 15.11.2012 AS SCR#17691 fixed form output with expressions where attribute was ANSI instead of Unicode
01.11.2006 AK SCR11825 Change the order of the column debit/credit

SQL_STMT_U.val:
select BANK_ADMNO, BANK_LEDG_NO, BANK_NAME, BANK_CURRENCY, LGCD_VALUEDATE, LGCD_AMOUNTDEBIT, LGCD_AMOUNTCREDIT, LGCD_DESCRIPTION, BANK_LEDG_NO_ADVANCES from :1/BANK join :1/LGCD on LGCD_ADMNO = BANK_ADMNO and LGCD_LDGR_NO = BANK_LEDG_NO_ADVANCES and LGCD_DEBITCREDITCHECK = 'N' and LGCD_DATE > ':2'
order by BANK_CURRENCY, BANK_ADMNO, BANK_LEDG_NO, LGCD_VALUEDATE, abs(LGCD_AMOUNTDEBIT-LGCD_AMOUNTCREDIT)
FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS
